Storm of Swords-Chapter 2\">Catelyn I</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Arya I</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_4\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 4\">Tyrion I</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_13\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 13\">Arya II</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Joshua-cairos-arya-starkjoshuacairs.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/Joshua-cairos-arya-starkjoshuacairs.jpg/300px-Joshua-cairos-arya-starkjoshuacairs.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"308\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/Joshua-cairos-arya-starkjoshuacairs.jpg/450px-Joshua-cairos-arya-starkjoshuacairs.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1b/Joshua-cairos-arya-starkjoshuacairs.jpg/600px-Joshua-cairos-arya-starkjoshuacairs.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Joshua-cairos-arya-starkjoshuacairs.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> looking at hanged men, by Joshua Cairós. © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Hot_Pie\" title=\"Hot Pie\">Hot Pie</a> head north after fleeing <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>, evading <a href=\"/index.php/Wolves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wolves\">wolves</a> and passing through a burned village. Using the map Arya stole from <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a>, they plan to find the <a href=\"/index.php/Trident\" title=\"Trident\">Trident</a> and follow the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>. They cross two rivers but are unable to identify them from the map. \n</p><p>Fearing pursuit, they ride for long hours and exhaust themselves. While Gendry stands guard, Arya falls asleep and dreams through the eyes of <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria_(direwolf)\" title=\"Nymeria (direwolf)\">a wolf</a>. In the dream, she sees four members of the <a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Brave Companions</a> pursuing in the rain, a pale <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lyseni</a>, an <a href=\"/index.php/Ibbenese\" title=\"Ibbenese\">Ibbenese</a> axeman, a <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishman</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Iggo\" title=\"Iggo\">Iggo</a>. The wolf and her pack ambush and ravage the four sellswords, quickly killing the first three. Iggo's horse kicks one of the wolves, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> cuts down another wolf. Arya's wolf, enraged by the deaths of two of her pack, knocks Iggo from his saddle and tears off his arm.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List\">Character List</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"66%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:2;\">\n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hot_Pie\" title=\"Hot Pie\">Hot Pie</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Iggo\" title=\"Iggo\">Iggo</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:22;\">\n<p><b>Mentioned</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Steelshanks_Walton\" title=\"Steelshanks Walton\">Steelshanks Walton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Vargo_Hoat\" title=\"Vargo Hoat\">Vargo Hoat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Syrio_Forel\" title=\"Syrio Forel\">Syrio Forel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dunsen\" title=\"Dunsen\">